<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Thanks for Joining SkillBridge</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#f1f5f9; font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#0f172a;">
  <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background-color:#f1f5f9; padding:24px 12px;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" style="max-width:620px; background:#ffffff; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius:16px; overflow:hidden;">
          <tr>
            <td style="background:linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9, #2563eb); padding:24px; text-align:center;">
              <h1 style="margin:0; font-size:22px; line-height:1.3; color:#ffffff;">Thanks for Joining SkillBridge</h1>
              <p style="margin:10px 0 0; color:#dbeafe; font-size:13px;">You are now part of our learning community</p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td style="padding:24px;">
              <p style="margin:0 0 12px; font-size:15px; color:#334155;">Hello <strong style="color:#0f172a;"><%= name || 'Learner' %></strong>,</p>
              <p style="margin:0 0 14px; font-size:14px; color:#475569; line-height:1.7;">
                Thank you for subscribing to the SkillBridge newsletter. You will now receive updates on tutoring tips, platform news, learning resources, and new opportunities.
              </p>

              <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" style="background:#f8fafc; border:1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius:10px; margin-bottom:12px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:12px 14px; font-size:13px; color:#334155;">
                    <strong>What to expect:</strong>
                    <ul style="margin:8px 0 0 18px; padding:0; color:#475569; line-height:1.7;">
                      <li>Fresh learning tips and tutoring insights</li>
                      <li>Product updates and important announcements</li>
                      <li>Helpful resources to improve your learning journey</li>
                    </ul>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="margin:0; font-size:13px; color:#64748b; line-height:1.7;">
                If you ever want to unsubscribe, you can do it anytime from the newsletter unsubscribe endpoint or by contacting support at
                <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail || 'support@skillbridge.com' %>" style="color:#2563eb; text-decoration:none;">
                  <%= supportEmail || 'support@skillbridge.com' %>
                </a>
                .
              </p>

              <p style="margin:16px 0 0; font-size:14px; line-height:1.6; color:#334155;">
                Stay connected with SkillBridge and keep growing.<br />
                <strong style="color:#0f172a;">SkillBridge Team</strong>
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td style="background:#f8fafc; border-top:1px solid #e2e8f0; padding:12px; text-align:center;">
              <p style="margin:0; font-size:12px; color:#94a3b8;">&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> SkillBridge. All rights reserved.</p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
